    "content" : "So got round to fabricating and welding the front sub frame mounting points today (well the off-side one at any rate)\n<br> \n<br> I have lost count how many times i have put the front sub frame together to measure something to then have to take it apart to fabricate. Guess that's the game.\n<br> \n<br> \n<a href=\"https://flic.kr/p/2fyk1tR\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/47623523911_592dabf60a_k.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://flic.kr/p/2fyk1tR\" class=\"postlink\">Front sub frame mounting point</a> by \n<a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/78596025@N06/\" class=\"postlink\">Duke of Boots1966</a>, on Flickr\n<br> \n<br> \n<a href=\"https://flic.kr/p/2fyk1sZ\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/47623523861_dfe3b643f0_k.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://flic.kr/p/2fyk1sZ\" class=\"postlink\">Front sub frame mounting point</a> by \n<a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/78596025@N06/\" class=\"postlink\">Duke of Boots1966</a>, on Flickr\n<br> \n<br> \n<a href=\"https://flic.kr/p/Tq3kvW\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/33746246948_1e5b99d104_k.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://flic.kr/p/Tq3kvW\" class=\"postlink\">Front sub frame mounting point</a> by \n<a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/78596025@N06/\" class=\"postlink\">Duke of Boots1966</a>, on Flickr\n<br> \n<br> \n<a href=\"https://flic.kr/p/24WJrsv\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/40657133973_19350a2622_k.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://flic.kr/p/24WJrsv\" class=\"postlink\">Front sub frame mounting point</a> by \n<a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/78596025@N06/\" class=\"postlink\">Duke of Boots1966</a>, on Flickr",
    "lastEdited" : "Tue Apr 16, 2019 7:04 pm"
  }, {
